title: CableJive dockStubz+ Charge Converter and 30-pin Pass Through Adapter for iPhone, iPod, and iPad
description: Fit all cases and work with all docks.You want protection for your iPhone, iPod, or iPad, but taking the case, cover, or skin off every time you need to dock it or connect an accessory is a pain! Avoid the hassle with dockStubz+, a small 1.3 inches (3.5 cm) tall 30-pin pass-through adapter that lets you use all the functionality of your device, without the pain and risk of removing its protection. Save yourself the trouble, and leave the case on while you dock with the dockStubz+.This is the dockStubz+ model, which includes charge conversion circuitry for older docks and accessories that use Firewire for charging. Safely connect your mobile device to any dock and get the charging you need. Also includes a micro USB port on the side for power injection & split off.All products purchased from CableJive include our warranty. If there is anything wrong with your product, please contact our service department. We're happy to help.
